snippet.title: The Wavy Tube Man Chronicles Official Windows 8 Launch Trailer
snippet.description: This is the official launch trailer for the single most important video game ever created.  The Wavy Tube Man Chronicles.  As seen in the Best Selling Xbox 360 title, The Gunstrigner, WTMC now comes to you on the Windows 8 and Surface Tablet platforms. Get your copy today for the low low price of $1.49 in the Windows Store.
